┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           ANDROID COROUTINES CHEAT SHEET                          │
├────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ START A COROUTINE      │                                          │
│  launch { }            │ Fire-and-forget, returns Job             │
│  async { }             │ Returns result via Deferred<T>           │
│  withContext(D) { }    │ Switch thread, returns result            │
│  coroutineScope { }    │ Child scope, waits for all children      │
│  supervisorScope { }   │ Child scope, isolated failures           │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ SCOPES                 │                                          │
│  viewModelScope        │ ViewModel lifecycle                      │
│  lifecycleScope        │ Activity/Fragment lifecycle              │
│  viewLifecycleOwner    │ Fragment VIEW lifecycle                  │
│  .lifecycleScope       │                                          │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ DISPATCHERS            │                                          │
│  Dispatchers.Main      │ UI updates                               │
│  Dispatchers.IO        │ Network, DB, file I/O                    │
│  Dispatchers.Default   │ CPU-intensive work                       │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ FLOW                   │                                          │
│  flow { emit() }       │ Create cold stream                       │
│  .collect { }          │ Start and consume stream                 │
│  .map / .filter        │ Transform values                         │
│  .flowOn(IO)           │ Run upstream on background thread        │
│  .stateIn(scope)       │ Convert to StateFlow                     │
│  .catch { }            │ Handle errors in flow                    │
│  .debounce(500)        │ Wait before emitting                     │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ HOT FLOWS              │                                          │
│  MutableStateFlow(v)   │ State holder, always has value           │
│  MutableSharedFlow()   │ Event bus, no initial value              │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ CANCELLATION           │                                          │
│  job.cancel()          │ Cancel a coroutine                       │
│  job.cancelAndJoin()   │ Cancel and wait                          │
│  isActive              │ Check if coroutine is still active       │
│  withTimeout(ms) { }   │ Throws on timeout                        │
│  withTimeoutOrNull { } │ Returns null on timeout                  │
├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ BEST PRACTICES         │                                          │
│  ✅                    │ Use viewModelScope/lifecycleScope         │
│  ✅                    │ Switch to IO for blocking calls           │
│  ✅                    │ Use repeatOnLifecycle in Fragments        │
│  ✅                    │ Use stateIn for expensive flows           │
│  ✅                    │ Re-throw CancellationException            │
│  ❌                    │ Never use GlobalScope                     │
│  ❌                    │ Never block Main with Thread.sleep        │
│  ❌                    │ Never swallow CancellationException       │
